<div class="overlayText">
<div class="textContainer">
	<h2>
	Lead the transformation of retail
	
	</h2>
</div>
</div>



					 
						<div class="caption richtextContent">
	<p>Imagine choosing the latest styles to feature in a luxury retail assortment, planning the social media strategy for a new organic grocery chain or launching a startup to run your own e-commerce business. Join the next generation of leaders in a dynamic and evolving sector of the global economy.</p> 
<p>A BComm in Retail Management will give you a solid foundation in buying, merchandising, strategic planning, retail technologies, operations management, customer experience design through in-store, online, and mobile channels, global issues, brand or category management, social media and much more. Use industry-leading software to design product displays, analyze how consumers engage with brands across social media and visualize business intelligence or geographic data.</p>
</div>
						    
					
